  "info": {
    "name": "Transaction Management System",
    "description": "Complete API collection for Transaction Management System with distributed transaction guarantees and comprehensive audit logging.\n\n## Features\n- âœ… Distributed transactions with Saga pattern\n- âœ… Automatic audit logging for all operations\n- âœ… JWT-based authentication\n- âœ… Advanced filtering and pagination\n- âœ… Concurrent transaction support (5+ transactions in <70ms)\n- âœ… Comprehensive error handling\n- âœ… Interactive Swagger/OpenAPI documentation\n- âœ… Race condition fixes for distributed transactions\n\n## Quick Start\n1. Start services: `docker-compose up -d`\n2. Run 'Login' request to get JWT token (auto-saved to variables)\n3. Explore other endpoints with automatic authentication\n4. View interactive API docs in Swagger UI\n\n## Services & Documentation\n- **Transaction Service**: http://localhost:3000\n- **Audit Service**: http://localhost:3001\n- **Transaction Swagger UI**: http://localhost:3000/documentation\n- **Transaction OpenAPI JSON**: http://localhost:3000/documentation/json\n- **Audit Swagger UI**: http://localhost:3001/documentation\n- **Audit OpenAPI JSON**: http://localhost:3001/documentation/json\n\n## Test Coverage\nâœ… 41/41 E2E tests passing (100%)\nâœ… Full CRUD operations\nâœ… Distributed transaction handling\nâœ… Audit log verification\nâœ… Rollback scenarios\nâœ… Concurrency testing\nâœ… Authentication & authorization\nâœ… Input validation\n\n## Recent Updates (2025-11-11)\n- Fixed distributed transaction race conditions\n- Enhanced Swagger documentation with detailed schemas\n- Fixed querystring validation for pagination\n- Improved concurrent transaction handling\n- All tests now passing with zero timeouts",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json",
    "version": "2.1.0"
  },
